OL,11,     Gever, all four teams leave Zaamin
OL,12,     GNational Park and race towards
OL,13,     Gthe next checkpoint, Almaty,
OL,14,     GKazakhstan's former Soviet-era
OL,15,     Gcapital.
OL,16,G2100FMasterChef
OL,17,     GThe week closes with the third
OL,18,     Gquarter-final as the six best
OL,19,     Gcooks of the week return, taking
OL,20,     Gon two more challenges to prove
OL,21,     Gthey have the nerve and skill to
